<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又和唐僧一起继续去西天取经了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父！”悟空说，“我在普陀山的时候，想了很多。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我意识到伤人是不对的。我不会再那么做了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，你能这样想，我很高兴。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以慢点儿走吗？”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我累了，天太热了！”悟空笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看来我走后，八戒还是老样子，喜欢抱怨啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟净擦了擦头上的汗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52555</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太热了。我们应该休息一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的。”唐僧说，“我不明白为什么这么热。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在又不是夏天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68157</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他们走到了一个村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个老人让他们在自己家里过夜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那天傍晚，大家在一起吃晚饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里一直都这么热吗？”八戒问。老人点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火焰山在这附近，所以这里一直都很热。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。我更想继续走。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这样我们就可以快点儿远离这高温了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要去哪里？”老人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去西天。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老人皱了皱眉说：“你们不能从这里走。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都放下了碗，看着老人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117198</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么呢？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火焰山在西面。”老人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们是不可能翻过火焰山的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们就绕过去。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老人摇摇头说：“火焰山周围都被火焰覆盖着，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>并且向北和南延伸。你们不可能绕过去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那我们就等到暴风雨来的时候再走。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“暴风雨会扑灭火焰的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行。”老人说，“那火焰是有法力的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>只有一个人可以扑灭它。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁？”悟净问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“铁扇公主。”老人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她有一把扇子，可以扇灭火焰。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那扇子是用蒲葵做的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空站起来。“铁扇公主住在哪里？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我让她扑灭火焰。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她不会听你的。”老人说，“她很厉害。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空双臂交叉，说道：“我也非常厉害的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>告诉我她住在哪里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204350</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老人告诉了悟空铁扇公主的住处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到了空中飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209086</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老人大吃一惊。“他是个神仙！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空很快到了铁扇公主住的山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他上前敲了敲洞门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开门！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞门开了。一个高大的女人出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿着一把大扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235352</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239596</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是孙悟空。我想借你的扇子用用。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孙悟空？哼！”铁扇公主怒吼道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246356</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是我最大的敌人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空很疑惑地问：“我？为什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主瞪着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我丈夫是牛魔王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他以前是你的朋友。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们的儿子是红孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265405</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为你，红孩儿被观音菩萨囚禁！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265406</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。“红孩儿又不是囚犯！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他现在是观音菩萨的弟子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273183</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不再是妖怪了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>铁扇公主又大叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就更可恶了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就借你的扇子用一小会儿，行不行？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！”铁扇公主说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那好，我能和牛魔王说几句话吗？”悟空问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他现在不在。”铁扇公主说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302025</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，马上给我离开这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空生气了。“我才不会走呢。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除非你把扇子借......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼！铁扇公主挥舞扇子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一阵强风刮过，悟空不见了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>